Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.99,0:00:42.24,GEM,,0,0,0,,{\fs22}{\i1}I gaze at the sky where tomorrow should arrive,\NMy heart, lost and wandering, can’t decide its stride{\i0}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.24,0:00:52.75,GEM,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A bird beside me took flight,\NI wonder if it found somewhere the light{\i0}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.75,0:01:03.43,GEM,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, won’t you let me\Nride on your back as well?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.43,0:01:10.63,GEM,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then leave me\Nat the highest place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:14.80,GEM,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Take me far away\Nfrom any kindness{\i0}
